        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drizzle<strong> </strong>some<strong> olive oil</strong> through the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>spaghetti</strong> and give it a good mix up (this stops the pasta from sticking together!)</p>",
