      "instruction": "<p>Once the fish is cooked, break it apart into bite-sized pieces with a wooden spoon, then add your <strong>soft cheese</strong> and the juice of <strong>half </strong>your<strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>lemon[s]</strong></p>",
